IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. ICSAUTHZ.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-RESPONSE-CODE      PIC X(02).
01 WS-AUDIT-FLAG         PIC X VALUE 'N'.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    PERFORM VALIDATE-CARD
    PERFORM APPLY-SPEND-CONTROL
    PERFORM CALL-CORE-AUTH
    IF WS-RESPONSE-CODE = '00'
        MOVE 'Y' TO WS-AUDIT-FLAG
    END-IF
    GOBACK.
